# NAME: Steam_Proxy
# AUTHOR: blackmatrix7
# REPO: https://github.com/blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script
# UPDATED: 2025-03-18
# DESCRIPTION: Steam需要代理的域名 - 部分功能/区域限制
# HOST-SUFFIX: 22
# TOTAL: 22

# Steam好友列表/聊天服务器（部分地区不稳定）
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com
HOST-SUFFIX,steam-chat.com

# Steam创意工坊（部分地区访问慢）
HOST-SUFFIX,steamworkshop.download

# Steam市场（部分区域限制）
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/market

# Steam好友邀请
HOST-SUFFIX,s.team

# Steam登录验证
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/openid
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/oauth

# Steam云存档同步（部分地区慢）
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcloud.ugc

# Steam远程同乐
HOST-SUFFIX,steamremoteplay.net

# Steam匹配服务器（部分游戏）
HOST-SUFFIX,steamgamesnetwork.com

# Steam成就系统
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/stats

# Steam个人资料
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/id
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/profiles

# Steam组/论坛
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/groups
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/discussions

# Steam艺术作品/截图
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/sharedfiles
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/workshop

# Steam指南
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/guides

# Steam评测
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/reviews

# Steam活动
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/broadcast

# Steam新闻
HOST-SUFFIX,steamcommunity.com/games

# Steam API
HOST-SUFFIX,api.steampowered.com
